comments: McDaniels (TOR) reaches in and initiates contact to White's (BOS) arm during the drive that affects his SQBR.
White (BOS) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Barnes (TOR) during the drive.
Hauser (BOS) gains possession of the ball with his foot out of bounds.
McDaniels (TOR) moves alongside White's (BOS) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) slides his pivot foot before the release of his dribble.
Brown (BOS) jumps towards Barnes (TOR) and places his off-arm against him as he makes the pass, but the contact is marginal and does not dislodge Barnes from his position.
Replay review of the foul called on Kornet (BOS) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Kornet initiates illegal contact with Schroder's (TOR) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) commits a take foul on Holiday (BOS).
Siakam (TOR) does not release the throw-in within five seconds.
Barnes (TOR) establishes himself in Brissett's (BOS) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Brissett (BOS) avoids making contact to Barnes' (TOR) arm and legally contests the driving shot attempt.
Schroder (TOR) commits a take foul on Holiday (BOS).
White (BOS) reaches in and initiates illegal contact with Siakam (TOR).  After communicating with the Replay Center, the foul occurs with 1.4 seconds remaining and the game clock is reset.
